    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a technique called "QNAME minimisation" to improve DNS privacy, where the DNS resolver no longer always sends the full original QNAME and original QTYPE to the upstream name server.  This document obsoletes RFC 7816.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
